  (license) => {
  if (license == 'None') {
    return `None`;
  }
  else if  (license == 'MIT') {
  return `![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)`;
  }
  else if (license == 'Mozilla 2.0') {
    return `![License: MPL 2.0](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MPL%202.0-brightgreen.svg)`;
  }
}
